# Web Frontend (Next.js)

Dashboard: viewer (digest okuma, chat) + admin (7 yönetim sayfası). SSR auth guard + client hydration.

## Klasör Yapısı (özet)

```
apps/web/src/
  app/           → App Router sayfaları
  components/    → ui/ (atom) + common/ (organism)
  hooks/         → React Query hooks
  lib/           → api-client, auth, utils
  types/         → TS tipleri (shared ile uyumlu)
```

## SSR vs CSR

- Auth gerektiren layout: middleware token kontrolü → redirect `/login`
- Digest listesi/detay: SSR veya RSC + client cache (React Query)
- Admin formlar: CSR + mutation

## API Client

Axios instance: base URL env'den, `withCredentials: true` (cookie). 401 → refresh cycle → retry; refresh fail → `/login`.

## State

- Server state: **TanStack Query** (cache, invalidation)
- Client state: React Context (auth user, theme minimal)

## Güvenlik

- Token httpOnly cookie — `localStorage` yasak
- Admin route'ları middleware + `RoleGate` component (UX only)
- CSP ve security headers middleware'de

## Anti-pattern'ler

- Fetch doğrudan component içinde (hook/service kullan)
- Viewer'da admin API çağrısı (backend zaten 403 döner ama UX kötü)
- `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` (digest HTML sanitize pipeline gerekir)

